INSERT INTO `n_fg_faqs` (`id`, `title`, `content`) VALUES
(1, 'GameTwist for free?', 'You can play all of the games on offer at GameTwist for free! You just have to sign up for an account - at no charge.\r\n\r\nIf you would like to receive more Twists than your fellow gamers, as well as have the ability to download 10 free games on your mobile phone and organise your own tournaments, then we recommend you pick up a Gold subscription. Details can be found in the Gold subscription FAQ.'),
(2, 'Gold Subscription', 'Why get a GOLD subscription?\r\n\r\nGOLD subscribers\r\n\r\nreceive thousands of additional Twists free with every subscription\r\ncan organise their own tournaments\r\n\r\nHow much does a GOLD subscription cost?\r\n\r\n1 month - €8.50\r\n1 year - €72'),
(3, 'Twists', 'Playing games on the platform earns you additional Twists. Twists act as bonus points at GameTwist and are used for placing stakes in various games on the platform. As Twists are bonus points, you cannot redeem them for money.\r\n\r\nTwists can be earnt by performing various activities on the platform (see table below). You can also buy Twist packs at the GameTwist Shop.\r\n\r\nTwist rewards\r\n\r\nEvent	Twists	Conditions\r\nRegistration incl. confirmation of your e-mail address:	 5,000	  \r\nRegistration	 1,000	 When additional details are given\r\nGaming activity	 1,000 per day	 When at least one game is played to completion\r\nLogin	 500 per day	 For the 1st login of the day, if there are less than 100 Twists in the account\r\nGold Subscription (1 month)	 52,500	 At the time of subscription\r\nGold Subscription (3 months)	 157,500	 At the time of subscription\r\nGold Abo (12 months)	 630,000	 At the time of subscription\r\nOrganisation of a user tournament	 10,000	 When 10 or more users participate\r\n1st place in a user tournament	 10,000	 When 10 or more users participate\r\n2nd place in a user tournament	 5,000	 When 10 or more users participate\r\n3rd place in a user tournament	 2,500	 When 10 or more users participate'),
(4, 'Playing for Twists', 'You have the choice of playing for Twists or ranking list points in most of the games on the GameTwist website.  You don''t play for real money!  Twists are the bonus points which you receive by doing things such as participating in a tournament or achieving certain goals in a game.  You can also credit your account with Twists in the GameTwist Shop.\r\n\r\nYou can decide whether you want to play for Twists or ranking list points before entering a game in the game lobby.  To do so, simply click on either the ''Twists'' or ''Ranking List'' tab at the top of the game lobby window.\r\n\r\nYou can only play for Twists when in the Casino Area.  This is also true for Poker.\r\n\r\nCollecting and betting Twists\r\n\r\nYou will receive Twists for participating in various activities on the GameTwist platform. For more details, please click on Twists in the Help section.  You will also receive Twists if you subscribe to GameTwist.  Sign up for a subscription in the Shop.\r\n\r\nAlternatively, you can always credit your account with more Twists in the GameTwist Shop.\r\n\r\nPlaying for Twists\r\n\r\nSelect the ''Twists'' tab in the game lobby before entering the game.\r\n\r\nWhen playing for Twists, players'' skill levels are not shown as you are only playing for Twists, which have no effect on your skill level.  This is also the reason why all players are shown in white.\r\n\r\nWhen starting a new game, use the slider bar to set the Twist stakes.  A small percentage of this stake will be deducted as a table charge.  When looking to join a game, the Twist stakes for each game are shown under the participants in the table listings.  You will be shown how many Twists you have won/lost in a summary table at the end of each game.\r\n\r\nPlaying for Twists has no effect on your position in the ranking list or your skill level!\r\n\r\nPlaying for Ranking List Points    \r\n\r\nPlay for ranking list points by selecting the ''Ranking List'' tab in the game lobby.  Playing for ranking list points has no effect on your Twists.'),
