(11, 'Popular games', '<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Enter the fairytale world of the&nbsp;<strong>Magic Princess&nbsp;</strong>and fall under her spell. Search the kingdom for the Princess and you will be rewarded with Twists. Follow the magic and you&rsquo;ll find what you are looking for.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Magic Princess&nbsp;</strong>is a slot machine, or one-armed bandit, at which you can multiply your Twists relatively simply. You can play with 5, 10 or 20 paylines across 5 reels. All winnings are paid from left to right.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	You can win even more Twists in the bonus games. Should 3 Magic Balls appear on the screen you will have the chance to double your stake. The bonus game allows you to win without the risk of losing.</p>\r\n', 11, '2013-01-19 05:44:09', '2013-01-19 09:00:00', '<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Enter the fairytale world of the&nbsp;<strong>Magic Princess&nbsp;</strong>and fall under her spell. Search the kingdom for the Princess and you will be rewarded with Twists. Follow the magic and you&rsquo;ll find what you are looking for.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Magic Princess&nbsp;</strong>is a slot machine, or one-armed bandit, at which you can multiply your Twists relatively simply. You can play with 5, 10 or 20 paylines across 5 reels. All winnings are paid from left to right.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	You can win even more Twists in the bonus games. Should 3 Magic Balls appear on the screen you will have the chance to double your stake. The bonus game allows you to win without the risk of losing.</p>\r\n', 0),
